        \ ensure the reply appears in the same conversation on the recipient's end.\
        \ It also prefixes the subject line with 'Re:' and correctly populates the\
        \ recipient list based on the original sender. Behavioral notes: You provide\
        \ the new text content for the reply body. The context and history of the\
