        \ answering a colleague's question without starting a new thread, acknowledging\
        \ the receipt of a report or document, and continuing a long-running professional\
        \ discussion with a client or partner. Keywords: email reply, thread management,\
        \ Outlook response, conversation flow, automated reply, message threading,\
        \ direct response, mail thread continuity, context preservation. Caveats:\
