        \ any manual back-and-forth negotiation, finding the very first available\
        \ slot for an urgent 'hotfix' meeting, and optimizing a team's weekly sync\
        \ to ensure maximum attendance. Keywords: meeting coordination, availability\
        \ search, scheduling optimization, Outlook calendar, slot finding, free/busy\
        \ analysis, schedule matching, optimal time finding, participant availability,\
        \ meeting planning. Caveats: This tool primarily works for internal participants\
        \ within the same organization or for external users who have explicitly shared\
